  "2026-06-06T20:41:38.132Z",unknown,"Execution kickoff: continuing active open-item work under pm-ugqx (linked pm-u9d0) with scoped implementation for afterCommand coverage hardening plus GitHub code-scanning report visibility, followed by full verification, temp-dir manual smoke, PR loop, and merge."
  "2026-06-06T21:26:52.147Z",unknown,"Verification evidence (continuation cycle):\n- Local gates passed: pnpm build, pnpm typecheck, node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage => 2528 tests, 100% statements/branches/functions/lines.\n- Focused regression suite passed: node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/extensions-runtime.spec.ts tests/integration/extension-hooks.integration.spec.ts tests/unit/sdk-index.spec.ts (48 tests).\n- Security scan passed: pnpm security:scan => no credential-like secrets detected.\n- Vulnerability scan passed with timeout override: PNPM_FETCH_TIMEOUT=600000 pnpm audit --json => 0 vulnerabilities (info/low/moderate/high/critical all zero).\n- Dependency updates: PNPM_FETCH_TIMEOUT=600000 pnpm outdated --format json => only commander 14.0.3 -> latest 15.0.0; still intentionally pinned to 14.x because project engine floor is Node >=20 while commander 15 requires newer Node runtime.\n- GitHub triage via gh: open issues [], open PRs [], open dependabot alerts [], open secret-scanning alerts [].\n- Code-scanning endpoint currently returns 404 no analysis found; remediation delivered by adding .github/workflows/codeql.yml so analysis uploads once the branch/PR workflow runs.\n- Sentry/telemetry gate passed: node scripts/release/sentry-telemetry-gate.mjs --json --telemetry-mode required --max-critical 0 --max-high 0 --max-telemetry-error-rate 10 --max-telemetry-missing-error-rows 0 => ok true, critical 0, high 0, telemetry finish_error_rate_pct 1.89, missing_error_code_rows 0.\n- Manual temp-dir smoke passed (fresh workspace): init/create/update/comments/list/contracts/health/validate/close/list-closed all succeeded for item pm-r1kj. Temp path: /tmp/tmp.O7PQ3KcCps.\n- Changelog contract verified with package-owned generator check path: node dist/cli.js changelog generate --output CHANGELOG.md --title \\\"Changelog\\\" --mode replace --all-release-tags --status closed --item-url-base https://github.com/unbraind/pm-cli/blob/main/.agents/pm --check => unchanged."
